Lesson 46 单词句型讲解

lift    举起
    Can you lift this heavy case?
    电梯(英式直梯，美式：elevator)
    There are thirteen people in this lift,it's overweight.
    电梯里有13人，超重啦

cake    蛋糕，可数名词

biscuit 饼干，可数名词






















